additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Irritant. This product contains ingredients which may cause skin irritation to certain individuals. A preliminary test according to the accompanying directions should be made before use. This product must not be used for dyeing eyelashes or eyebrows; to do so may be injurious to the eye. Keep out of reach of children. Read safety directions before use. Can cause allergic reactions - follow the safety warnings. Hair colourants can cause severe allergic reactions. Read and follow instructions. This product is not intended for use on persons under the age of 16.
